review.reviewBody: All the food was nicely packed and very delicious. However, for the expensive pricing the portions were extremely small and disappointing.
Love the black bean tacos! And their parm fries with dip are my favourite!!   The tofu lettuce wraps are so fresh aswell!! My fave restaurant to order off of!
The food was packaged very nicely and was still hot, it looked like it was handled with care. It was also very tasty and reasonably priced. Will order again it was a pleasure.
Fresh smashed guacamole was delicious! I licked the plate!
lacked flavor and for the price very disappointing!
